1
00:00:00,460 --> 00:00:02,840
I tried doing my own makeup...

2
00:00:03,170 --> 00:00:05,760
I wish Yuki could see it.

3
00:00:06,090 --> 00:00:08,880
I wonder if I'll run into him somewhere...

4
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:10,220
Oh, Yuki...

5
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:15,390
Why am I hiding again?

6
00:00:15,390 --> 00:00:20,400
(Yuki and Natsu are chatting happily.)

7
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:24,650
What are they talking about?
They look so happy.

8
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:31,200
So, how's the makeup practice going?
Think he has a shot at being the festival prince?

9
00:00:31,910 --> 00:00:36,330
Of course. He's got the best features, after all.

10
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:38,330
And he's got a great personality.

11
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:40,290
Ooh!

12
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:43,080
This was a thank-you gift from him.

13
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:45,460
Oh, that's nice!

14
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,340
It's so cute!

15
00:00:47,710 --> 00:00:50,720
Yeah.
It really is.

16
00:00:51,220 --> 00:00:53,470
Both this and him.

17
00:00:53,470 --> 00:00:55,930
You seem really happy.

18
00:00:57,020 --> 00:00:59,480
(That's the handkerchief I gave him...)

19
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:01,850
Don't tell me...
Are they making fun of me?

20
00:01:01,850 --> 00:01:04,940
No, that's not it.
Yuki wouldn't do that.

21
00:01:05,770 --> 00:01:07,320
Hee hee hee.

22
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:09,740
This just makes me want to see him even more.
